---
title: T-Pain’s Spicy Garlic Chicken Sandwiches with Hot Like the Tropics Pineapple Slaw
description: If you’re feeling like you want to get On a Boat to the tropics to live the Good Life, it’s lucky for you that T-Pain got on board with his limited-edition twist on a spicy chicken sandwich! Garlic butter-brushed brioche buns are piled high with spicy, tangy shredded chicken tossed with hot sauce. Loaded on top are tomato slices and a savory-sweet pineapple-lime cabbage slaw for crisp, cool contrast. Add a little more garlic butter on top and extra slaw on the side to round out this twisty, fiery number.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64bfcc7d8e7c223eb5b363e0-a42864c6.jpeg
